author: CNN
description: Delays are getting worse across the country as air traffic controller staffing problems persist despite cuts to flights mandated by the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA). FAA operations noted 25 reports of staffing problems so far on Friday, as well as some substantial delays. CNN's Jake Tapper hosts "The Points Guy" Brian Kelly to discuss what rights you have as a potential victim of delayed and cancelled flights amid a historic government shutdown. #CNN #News
title: 'Be on the offense': Your rights as victim of delayed, cancelled flights according to Brian Kelly

author: CNN
description: Democratic Rep. Jared Golden of Maine announced Wednesday that he would not seek reelection in 2026. CNN's Dana Bash dives into the reasons why, and what that says about the state of US politics.
title: Dana Bash on why Rep. Jared golden is leaving congress

description: The nominations for the 68th Grammy Awards have finally arrived ahead of the ceremony taking place on February 1, 2026. CNN's Elizabeth Wagmeister breaks down who got the most nominations, and who didn’t make the cut. #cnn #news #grammys #2026grammys

author: CNN
description: President Donald Trump keeps touting the fact that Walmart’s promotional Thanksgiving meal basket is cheaper this year than it was last year. title: Fact Check: Trump's Walmart Thanksgiving basket claim

author: CNN
description: Pittsburgh dad AJ Owen received an unexpected envelope filled with thousands of dollars after videos of his front yard food pantry went viral. Owen and his kids were motivated by news that the Trump administration would halt SNAP benefits as part of the government shutdown. The administration announced Friday it would fully fund food stamp benefits for November to comply with a federal court order.
title: Man receives thousands of dollars after front yard food pantry touches hearts

description:

Errol Louis is the Political Anchor of Spectrum News and NY1, and he’s here to tell David Chalian how Mamdani rewrote the political playbook in Gotham.

#cnn #news #politics #davidchalian #errollouis #nyc #newyork #newyorkcity #mamdani #zohranmamdani

author: CNN
description:
Japan’s new prime minister, Sanae Takaichi, made headlines for her whirlwind diplomatic debut - attending APEC and ASEAN summits and hosting President Donald Trump, but it was her informal interactions with world leaders that sparked debate at home. Critics called them unprofessional while supporters praised her approachable style while suggesting a gendered double standard to the criticism.

#CNN #News #Japan
title: How Takaichi's big week divided the Japanese public

author: CNN
description:
From detecting heartbeat irregularities to flagging signs of hypertension and hearing loss, devices like the Apple Watch are becoming unexpected players in preventive care. In a conversation taped before a live audience at The Paley Center for Media in New York, Dr. Sanjay Gupta talks with Dr. Sumbul Desai, Apple’s Vice President of Health, about how these tools are quietly transforming the way we think of health – and putting more control in the hands of users, one tap at a time.

Listen to the full episode on CNN's Chasing Life podcast: http://swap.fm/l/clsgyt110725

#cnn #news #health #wearabletech #wearables #medicine #sanjaygupta #drsanjaygupta #apple
title: Can your smart watch actually help you live longer? | Chasing Life
